(2, 'Fintown', '/platformLogo/Fintown.png', '[\"Czech Republic\"]', '[\"P2P lending\"]', '[\"Real estate\"]', '2023', 'N/A', '[\"English\",\"German\",\"Spanish\",\"Italian\",\"Czech\",\"Latvian\"]', NULL, 'https://www.fintown.eu/', '50 EUR', 'N/A', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Fintown is a crowdfunding platform based in the Czech Republic that specializes in P2P lending for real estate projects. Founded in 2023, Fintown is powered by Vihorev Group and aims to provide a convenient and safe investment opportunity in European real estate developments.\n\nOne of the main features of Fintown is its focus on real estate projects, which gives investors the chance to diversify their portfolios and potentially earn stable returns. The platform offers investment in various real estate developments, allowing investors to support projects that align with their investment goals.\n\nFintown operates primarily in Europe and offers multiple language options, including English, German, Spanish, Italian, Czech, and Latvian. This multilingual approach ensures that investors from different countries can easily navigate and understand the platform.\n\nTo start investing on Fintown, users must first register and acknowledge the potential risks associated with investing. Only registered users who meet these criteria are eligible to invest on the platform. The minimum investment amount is 50 EUR, making it accessible to a wide range of investors.\n\nHowever, specific details regarding the advertised return are not provided. Nonetheless, Fintown positions itself as a reliable platform for real estate investing, emphasizing trust as a key factor for their clients.\n\nTo learn more about Fintown and explore potential investment opportunities, interested individuals can visit their official website at https://www.fintown.eu/.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Only registered users who understand the potential risks associated with investing are eligible to invest on our platform.', 'fintown', '2023-0