(3, 'Unbroken', '/platformLogo/Unbroken.png', '[\"Ukraine\"]', '[\"Donation\"]', '[\"Social cause\"]', '2022', 'N/A', '[\"English\",\"Ukrainian\"]', NULL, 'https://unbroken.org.ua/', '1 EUR', 'N/A', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Unbroken is a crowdfunding platform based in Ukraine, founded in 2022. It operates as a donation-based platform, catering to social causes. The platform serves as a powerful support system for individuals affected by the war in Ukraine, particularly those in Lviv.\n\nThe primary language used on the platform is both English and Ukrainian, ensuring accessibility for a wide range of users. Unbroken\'s website, located at https://unbroken.org.ua/, provides all necessary information and resources for potential donors.\n\nOne notable aspect of Unbroken is its emphasis on resilience and strength. The platform\'s name represents the indomitable spirit of Ukrainians who, despite losing everything such as their homes, families, and childhood, remain unbroken. The city of Lviv specifically plays a pivotal role as a humanitarian hub, providing aid to those fleeing the war.\n\nUnbroken welcomes donations from both personal and corporate parties, making it accessible to individuals as well as socially responsible businesses. The minimum investment required is 1 EUR, ensuring that anyone can contribute to the cause.\n\nWhile Unbroken does not offer an advertised financial return on investment, it provides a platform for individuals and organizations to offer much-needed support to those affected by the war in Ukraine. It serves as a catalyst for positive change and aims to rebuild and uplift the lives of those who have been devastated by the conflict.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Personal, Corporate', 'unbroken', '2023-08-08 09:32:54', '2023-08-08 09:32:54'),
