(69, 'FINEXITY', '/platformLogo/FINEXITY.png', '[\"Germany\"]', '[\"Debt\"]', '[\"Real estate\"]', '2019', 'HRB 153232', '[\"German\\nEnglish\"]', NULL, 'https://finexity.com/', '500 EUR', '5-10.4%', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Anyone who meets the minimum investment requirement of 500 EUR can invest in FINEXITY, a crowdfunding platform based in Germany. Founded in 2019, FINEXITY specializes in debt investment within the real estate industry. The platform brings together investors and real estate assets, offering an opportunity for individuals to invest in real estate projects and properties.\n\nOne of the noteworthy features of FINEXITY is its use of blockchain technology to digitize assets in a legally secure manner. This digitization process helps reduce entry barriers for investors, making real estate investments more accessible. Additionally, FINEXITY provides a secondary market where investors can trade their investments, increasing liquidity and offering flexibility for investment management.\n\nThe platform is available in German and English, catering to a wider international audience. With a minimum investment requirement of 500 EUR, FINEXITY welcomes both small and large investors. Advertised returns on investment range from 5% to 10.4%, providing potential for attractive earnings.\n\nOverall, FINEXITY offers a modern crowdfunding solution for individuals interested in investing in real estate. Its utilization of blockchain technology, coupled with its user-friendly platform and international accessibility, makes it an appealing option for anyone seeking to participate in the real estate market with a relatively lower investment threshold.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL, 'finexity', '2023-08-08 09:32:54', '2023-08-08 09:32:54'),
