(71, 'Ecozins', '/platformLogo/Ecozins.png', '[\"Germany\"]', '[\"Debt\"]', '[\"Green energy\"]', '2019', ' HRB 6799', '[\"German\"]', NULL, 'https://www.ecozins.de/', '250 EUR', '3-3.5%', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Ecozins is a crowdfunding platform based in Germany that specializes in debt-based investments in the green energy industry. Founded in 2019, the platform allows private investors to easily invest online in projects that generate returns and contribute to climate protection. \n\nThe primary focus of Ecozins is on investments in plants that produce climate-neutral energy, which often require significant capital. For example, the platform supports investments in wind farms, which are known for their effectiveness in reducing carbon emissions and providing renewable energy. \n\nEcozins operates primarily in Germany and the platform\'s website is available in German. The minimum investment required to participate is 250 EUR, making it accessible to a wide range of private investors. The advertised return on investments ranges from 3% to 3.5%, providing attractive potential returns for investors, while also supporting projects that contribute to a greener future. \n\nBy providing a user-friendly platform and connecting investors with sustainable energy projects, Ecozins aims to create a community of investors who are motivated to protect the climate and make responsible investment choices. They offer individuals the opportunity to support green energy initiatives and make a positive impact on the environment while also potentially earning a financial return.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, 'ecozins', '2023-08-08 09:32:54', '2023-08-08 09:32:54'),
(72, 'KlickOwn', '/platformLogo/KlickOwn.png', '[\"Germany\"]', '[\"Equity\"]', '[\"Real estate\"]', '2019', ' HRB 158577 B', '[\"German\",\"English\"]', NULL, 'https://www.klickown.com/', '10 EUR', 'up to 5%', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Anyone can invest in KlickOwn, as the platform is open to retail investors. The minimum investment required is 10 EUR, making it accessible to a wide range of individuals. KlickOwn focuses on the real estate industry, allowing investors to invest in European real estate projects. \n\nFounded in 2019 and based in Germany, KlickOwn operates as a crowdfunding platform that offers equity investments. Through its use of blockchain technology, KlickOwn tokenizes real estate assets, making investments in this sector more accessible and transparent. This decentralized online marketplace aims to revolutionize the way investors participate in the real estate market.\n\nKlickOwn\'s website is available in both German and English, catering to a broader audience. The platform\'s user-friendly interface allows investors to easily browse and choose from a variety of real estate projects to invest in. \n\nOne of the attractive features of KlickOwn is the advertised return on investment, which can be up to 5%. This potential return, combined with the low minimum investment requirement, makes it an enticing option for individuals interested in real estate investment.\n\nOverall, KlickOwn offers a decentralized and transparent platform for retail investors to invest in real estate projects in Europe, leveraging blockchain technology to tokenize assets and providing an accessible avenue for individuals to diversify their investment portfolios.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, 'klickown', '2023-08-08 09:32:54', '2023-08-08 09:32:54'),
