(75, 'Wisefund', '/platformLogo/Wisefund.png', '[\"Estonia\"]', '[\"P2P lending\"]', '[\"SME\"]', '2019', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://wisefund.eu/en/', '10 EUR', 'N/A', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Any individual or legal entity can invest in Wisefund, as long as they meet the minimum investment requirement of 10 EUR. The platform operates in Estonia and focuses on P2P lending within the SME industry. \n\nWisefund was founded in 2019 with the goal of building secure bridges between lenders and borrowers. The platform aims to provide valuable opportunities, secure transactions, and profitable returns for its users. \n\nOne of the key features of Wisefund is its mediation and monitoring of investments, which ensures a secure environment for both lenders and borrowers. This helps to minimize risks and increase the chances of successful investments. \n\nAlthough the exact advertised return is not mentioned, Wisefund promises to create a mutually favorable environment that benefits all parties involved. \n\nThe crowdfunding platform is accessible through its website, which is available in multiple languages. This enables users from various countries to participate in P2P lending on the platform. \n\nOverall, Wisefund is a relatively new crowdfunding platform that focuses on P2P lending in the SME industry. It aims to provide secure and profitable investment opportunities for lenders while assisting borrowers in obtaining the necessary funding for their businesses.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, 'wisefund', '2023-08-08 09:32:54', '2023-08-08 09:32:54'),
(76, 'neocredit.ch', '/platformLogo/neocredit.ch.png', '[\"Switzerland\"]', '[\"P2P lending\"]', '[\"SME\"]', '2018', NULL, '[\"English\",\"French\"]', NULL, 'https://neocredit.ch/', '100 CHF', 'N/A', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Neocredit.ch is a crowdfunding platform based in Switzerland that specializes in P2P lending for small and medium-sized enterprises (SMEs). The platform was founded in 2018 and aims to provide easy financing options for companies while offering an attractive investment opportunity for investors.\n\nNeocredit.ch operates as a crowdlending platform, allowing individuals to directly grant loans to Swiss SMEs with a minimum investment amount of just CHF 100. By enabling real crowdlending, the platform provides a win-win situation for both companies and investors.\n\nTo secure the financing of projects, neocredit.ch also partners with professional and institutional investors who contribute a partial amount. This ensures that the projects listed on the platform receive the necessary funding for their operations.\n\nThe platform is available in both English and French, catering to a larger audience of potential investors and SMEs. Neocredit.ch does not provide information on the advertised return, but it highlights the benefits of participating in the platform for both businesses and individuals looking to invest.\n\nWith a minimum investment of just CHF 100, neocredit.ch offers an accessible opportunity for individuals to support Swiss SMEs and participate in the growth potential of these businesses. The platform\'s website provides further information and details on how to get started with investing or applying for financing.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'From a minimum amount of just CHF 100, you can already grant loans directly to Swiss SMEs. This is how neocredit.ch enables real crowdlending! In order to secure the financing of the projects, professional and institutional investors give a partial amount. In this way, our two founding partners automatically participate in the financing of the selected projects on neocredit.ch.', 'neocredit.ch', '2023-08-08 09:32:54', '2023-08-08 09:32:54'),
(77, 'Сosmofunding', '/platformLogo/Сosmofunding.png', '[\"Switzerland\"]', '[\"Equity\"]', '[\"Real estate\",\"Startups\",\"SME\"]', '2018', NULL, '[\"English\",\"German\"]', NULL, 'https://www.cosmofunding.com/de-ch/', '1 EUR', 'N/A', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Сosmofunding is a crowdfunding platform based in Switzerland that was founded in 2018. The platform operates in the equity investment segment and focuses primarily on the real estate, startups, and SME industries. It offers a convenient and efficient way for investors and individuals seeking financing to connect with each other.\n\nThe platform is available in both English and German, ensuring accessibility for users from different language backgrounds. Cosmofunding\'s website, located at https://www.cosmofunding.com/de-ch/, provides detailed information on its services and offerings.\n\nThe minimum investment amount on Cosmofunding is 1 EUR, making it accessible to a wide range of potential investors. However, the advertised return on investments is not specified.\n\nCosmofunding caters to various types of investors, including financial intermediaries such as banks, securities dealers, pension funds, fund management companies, and life insurance companies. It also welcomes investment from authorities, large companies with professional treasury, as well as public-law institutions and foundations. The platform assures potential investors that further details and steps can be discussed in a personal conversation to clarify eligibility and facilitate the investment process.\n\nOverall, Cosmofunding provides a digital marketplace for efficient and transparent connections between investors and those seeking financing in the real estate, startups, and SME industries in Switzerland.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Your company basically qualifies as a financial intermediary (bank, securities dealer, pension fund, fund management company or SICAF/SICAV, life insurance company, KAG investment company, KAG asset manager), authority (federal, canton, municipality, public-law institutions/foundations) or large company with professional treasury as an investor for cosmofunding. We would be happy to clarify the details and further steps with you in a personal conversation.', 'сosmofunding', '2023-08-08 09:32:54', '2023-08-08 09:32:54'),
(78, 'Oblinor', '/platformLogo/Oblinor.png', '[\"Norway\"]', '[\"P2P lending\"]', '[\"Real estate\"]', '2018', 'N/A', '[\"Norwegian\"]', NULL, 'https://oblinor.no/', '1€', 'N/A', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Oblinor is a crowdfunding platform based in Norway that focuses on P2P lending in the real estate industry. Founded in 2018, Oblinor offers a digital platform that allows investors and project owners to connect and enter into agreements directly. As a non-banking institution, Oblinor provides a safe and flexible environment for investors and project owners to collaborate.\n\nThe platform is exclusively available in Norwegian, targeting individuals and legal entities who possess a Norwegian bank account and BankID. This requirement ensures that the users are verified and of legal age, at least 18 years or above.\n\nOblinor promotes transparency and accessibility by setting a low minimum investment amount of 1 Norwegian Krone. However, the advertised return on investment is not disclosed on their website.\n\nBy leveraging the power of crowdfunding, Oblinor empowers individuals and businesses to participate in the real estate market and generate financing options. Through their platform, investors have an opportunity to diversify their portfolio and support real estate projects they believe in, while project owners gain access to funding from a broader pool of interested parties.\n\nOverall, Oblinor\'s digital lending platform offers a unique solution in the Norwegian crowdfunding landscape, enabling direct agreements between investors and project owners in a secure and flexible manner.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Natural and legal persons:– with a Norwegian bank account; – with BankID; – over 18 years.', 'oblinor', '2023-08-08 09:32:54', '2023-08-08 09:32:54'),
