(81, 'MyKornerShop', '/platformLogo/MyKornerShop.png', '[\"France\"]', '[\"P2P lending\"]', '[\"Real estate\"]', '2018', '18005335', '[\"French\"]', NULL, 'https://www.mykornershop.com/', '1,000€', 'N/A', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'MyKornerShop is a crowdfunding platform based in France that specializes in P2P lending for real estate investments. Founded in 2018, the platform aims to enable local residents to collectively become owners of the walls of their neighborhood shops. The company\'s main objective is to contribute to the revival and development of local businesses and communities.\n\nAs a P2P lending platform, MyKornerShop allows any adult to invest, provided that they have completed their profile and their investment objectives align with the proposed projects. The platform utilizes a suitability questionnaire to determine if the investment objectives are compatible with the available projects. Additionally, investors need to provide identity documents, which are validated by the payment service provider MANGOPAY.\n\nMyKornerShop\'s website is available in French, reflecting its target market in France. The minimum investment amount on the platform is 1 unit, and the advertised return on investments is not specified.\n\nOne unique feature of MyKornerShop is that it allows companies to invest as well. To utilize this option, investors must select the \"company\" option when registering on the platform.\n\nOverall, MyKornerShop provides an online crowdfunding platform that offers individuals and companies the opportunity to support and invest in local neighborhood shops, contributing to the revitalization and growth of the community.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Any adult can invest on the platform, provided that they have completed their profile , that their investment objectives are in line with the proposed projects and that their identity documents are validated.The suitability of the investment objectives in relation to the proposed projects is determined by the suitability questionnaire .To be able to use the MANGOPAY payment services, it is necessary to provide their identity documents which are subject to validation with the payment service provider. It is possible to invest as a company, for this, you must choose the “company” option when registering.', 'mykornershop', '2023-08-08 09:32:54', '2023-08-08 09:32:54');
