(151, 'Beefordeal', '/platformLogo/Beefordeal.png', '[\"France\"]', '[\"Debt\"]', '[\"Real estate\"]', '2016', '17003713', '[\"French\"]', NULL, 'https://www.beefordeal.com/fr', '1,000 EUR', '8—12%', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Beefordeal is a French crowdfunding platform that was founded in 2016. It offers individuals and companies the opportunity to invest in real estate transactions and support real estate professionals in financing their operations. The platform operates as a debt-based crowdfunding platform, meaning investors lend money to real estate professionals in exchange for a fixed return.\n\nThe minimum investment on Beefordeal is 1,000 EUR, and the platform advertises a return range of 8-12%. To invest, individuals must meet certain criteria such as being of legal age, completing their investor profile, understanding the risks involved, and signing the General Conditions of Use. Legal persons are required to provide additional documents such as a K-Bis extract, articles of association, and declaration of beneficial owners.\n\nIt is important for potential investors to be aware of the risks associated with this type of investment and ensure that it aligns with their situation, objectives, and available resources. The decision to invest should be made independently after careful consideration.\n\nThe platform\'s website is available in French, and it provides a comprehensive overview of the investment opportunities and the process involved. For individuals and companies interested in real estate crowdfunding in France, Beefordeal offers a platform to connect with real estate professionals and contribute to their projects.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'For an individual , you will need to fulfill the following conditions: Be of legal age, complete their investor profile, understand the risks, sign the General Conditions of Use and send us your supporting documents.For legal persons , you will need to complete the list of these elements with a K-Bis extract, your articles of association and the declaration of beneficial owners.Reminder: It is essential to be aware of the possible risks of the investment and to ensure that the investment corresponds to your situation, your objectives and your resources. It is essential that the decision to invest be taken independently.', 'beefordeal', '2023-08-08 09:32:55', '2023-08-08 09:32:55'),
