(184, 'Mintos', '/platformLogo/Mintos.png', '[\"Latvia\"]', '[\"P2P lending\"]', '[\"Real estate\"]', '2016', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://www.mintos.com/en/', '10 EUR', 'N/A', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Mintos is a Latvian crowdfunding platform that was founded in 2016. It primarily focuses on Peer-to-Peer (P2P) lending in the real estate industry. The platform acts as a link between global investors and loans that are originated by various international alternative lending companies, which have been verified by Mintos.\n\nOne of the main attractions of Mintos is the opportunity it provides for investors to diversify their portfolios by investing in a wide range of consumer and business loans. The platform offers detailed information about each loan, allowing investors to make informed decisions. The minimum investment required to participate is just 10 EUR, making it accessible to investors with both small and large capital.\n\nWhile the exact advertised return is not mentioned, Mintos offers an enticing investment opportunity with its P2P lending model. This allows investors to earn interest on their investments by lending money directly to borrowers. Mintos also provides additional safety measures such as a Buyback Guarantee, which ensures that investors are protected against borrower defaults.\n\nMintos operates globally, connecting investors from all around the world. It is a user-friendly platform with a multilingual website, making it accessible to investors from different countries. Overall, Mintos offers a convenient and transparent crowdfunding platform for individuals interested in the P2P lending sector, with the potential for attractive returns on investment.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, 'mintos', '2023-08-08 09:32:55', '2023-08-08 09:32:55'),
(185, 'Bulkestate', '/platformLogo/Bulkestate.png', '[\"Latvia\"]', '[\"P2P lending\"]', '[\"Real estate\"]', '2016', 'N/A', '[\"English\"]', NULL, 'https://www.bulkestate.com/', '50 EUR', 'N/A', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Bulkestate is a real estate crowdfunding platform based in Latvia. Founded in 2016, the platform focuses on P2P lending in the real estate industry. The company offers investors the opportunity to participate in real estate investment projects and earn passive income.\n\nOne unique feature of Bulkestate is the option to buy real estate below market price through their group-buying platform. This allows investors to take advantage of exclusive deals and potentially increase their returns on investment.\n\nThe platform is available in English, making it accessible to a wider audience of international investors. The minimum investment required to participate is 50 EUR, providing an affordable entry point for both personal and corporate investors.\n\nWhile the advertised return is not specified, Bulkestate provides an avenue for investors to generate income through their real estate investments. The platform aims to streamline the process of real estate investing, making it more accessible and convenient for investors of various backgrounds.\n\nOverall, Bulkestate offers a user-friendly platform for individuals and businesses looking to diversify their investment portfolios through P2P lending in the real estate market.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Personal, Corporate', 'bulkestate', '2023-08-08 09:32:55', '2023-08-08 09:32:55'),
(186, 'JaeVee', '/platformLogo/JaeVee.png', '[\"United Kingdom\"]', '[\"Equity\"]', '[\"Real estate\"]', '2016', 'N/A', '[\"English\"]', NULL, 'https://www.jaevee.co.uk/', '20,000 EUR', 'N/A', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'JaeVee is a crowdfunding platform based in the United Kingdom that focuses on equity investment in the real estate industry. Founded in 2016, it is the first joint venture platform in the UK that connects property developers, main contractors, equity and mezzanine investors. The platform aims to address the country\'s housing shortage by enabling the delivery of high-quality homes.\n\nThe crowdfunding platform operates primarily in English and has a website at https://www.jaevee.co.uk/. The minimum investment amount on JaeVee is 20,000 EUR, and the advertised return is not specified. \n\nJaeVee caters to High Net Worth or Sophisticated Investors who are interested in investing in real estate projects. By bringing together various stakeholders, including property developers, contractors, and investors, JaeVee creates opportunities for joint ventures that help meet the housing demands in the UK.\n\nThis platform offers a unique investment avenue for individuals who are interested in the real estate sector but may not have the resources or expertise to engage in property development on their own. Through JaeVee, investors can contribute to the development of high-quality homes and potentially earn returns on their investments.\n\nOverall, JaeVee is a crowdfunding platform that facilitates equity investment in the real estate industry, connecting key players in the field to address the UK\'s housing shortage.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'High Net Worth or Sophisticated Investors.', 'jaevee', '2023-08-08 09:32:55', '2023-08-08 09:32:55'),
(187, 'Fundlift', '/platformLogo/Fundlift.png', '[\"Czech Republic\"]', '[\"P2P lending\"]', '[\"Real estate\"]', '2015', '06083269', '[\"English\",\"Czech\"]', NULL, 'https://www.fundlift.cz/', '5,000 CZK', 'N/A', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Fundlift is an investment-crowdfunding platform based in the Czech Republic. Founded in 2015, it focuses on P2P lending in the real estate industry. The platform serves as a connection between investors and ambitious projects seeking funding and marketing opportunities.\n\nFundlift is available in both English and Czech, making it accessible to a wider range of users. The platform boasts a user-friendly and convenient online interface, allowing investors to start with a minimum investment of 5,000 CZK. This low entry threshold ensures that almost anyone can participate.\n\nFundlift offers a unique opportunity for promising companies to receive funding and expand their operations. By leveraging the crowdfunding model, these companies can tap into a new source of capital and gain exposure to potential customers and partners. The platform acts as a marketing channel, facilitating the growth and visibility of the projects it hosts.\n\nWhile the exact advertised return is not specified, Fundlift provides investors with the potential to earn returns on their investments. This offers an attractive incentive for individuals looking to diversify their investment portfolios or support innovative projects within the real estate sector.\n\nFundlift is a versatile crowdfunding platform that caters to a broad audience, allowing everyone to invest and support promising projects. By bridging the gap between investors and companies, Fundlift facilitates growth and innovation in the real estate industry in the Czech Republic.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Everyone can. It’s simple and online, starting at 5 thousand CZK.', 'fundlift', '2023-08-08 09:32:55', '2023-08-08 09:32:55'),
(188, 'Italy-Crowd', '/platformLogo/Italy-Crowd.png', '[\"Italy\"]', '[\"P2P lending\"]', '[\"Real estate\"]', '2015', 'N/A', '[\"Italian\",\"English\"]', NULL, 'https://www.italy-crowd.com/it/home', '490 EUR', '6-12%', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Italy-Crowd is a crowdfunding platform based in Italy that specializes in P2P lending in the real estate industry. Founded in 2015, it was the first Italian real estate crowdfunding platform in the country. \n\nThe platform offers investment opportunities in the form of loans to real estate projects. Investors can participate individually or as a corporate entity. The minimum investment required is 490 EUR, and the platform promises an advertised return of 6-12%. \n\nOne notable feature of Italy-Crowd is its use of blockchain technology. It has recently undergone a renewal, and it is now the first native blockchain real estate lending platform in Europe. This integration of blockchain technology provides increased transparency, security, and efficiency in the lending process.\n\nItaly-Crowd operates in both Italian and English languages, making it accessible to a wider range of investors. Its website, https://www.italy-crowd.com/it/home, provides detailed information about the platform, its investment opportunities, and the investment process. \n\nOverall, Italy-Crowd provides individuals and corporations with a unique opportunity to invest in the Italian real estate market through its P2P lending platform. With the benefits of blockchain technology and the potential for attractive returns, Italy-Crowd is a promising platform for investors interested in the real estate industry.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Personal, Corporate', 'italy-crowd', '2023-08-08 09:32:55', '2023-08-08 09:32:55'),
(189, 'Loanboox', '/platformLogo/Loanboox.png', '[\"Switzerland\"]', '[\"Debt\",\"P2P lending\"]', '[\"Real estate\"]', '2015', 'CHE-283.230.900', '[\"English\",\"French\",\"Dutch\"]', NULL, 'https://loanboox.com/ch/de/home-de/', '1 EUR', 'N/A', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Loanboox is a crowdfunding platform based in Switzerland that specializes in debt-based P2P lending in the real estate industry. Founded in 2015, Loanboox offers a simple, transparent, safe, and low-cost way for borrowers and investors to engage in financing and investing. The platform operates in several languages including English, French, and Dutch.\n\nLoanboox is considered the leading European debt financing and management provider and aims to disrupt the traditional brokering methods prevalent in the industry. The platform\'s website, located at https://loanboox.com/ch/de/home-de/, provides all the necessary information for potential investors to get started.\n\nThe minimum investment amount on Loanboox is 1 EUR, making it accessible to a wide range of investors. While the platform does not advertise a specific return on investment, it offers numerous investment opportunities in the real estate sector.\n\nOnly legal entities based in Switzerland with a UID entry and a professional treasury department are eligible to invest through Loanboox. This includes insurers, pension funds, banks, professional asset managers, family offices, and public corporations. Loanboox aims to provide a secure environment for investments, ensuring both borrowers and investors benefit from their services.\n\nOverall, Loanboox stands out for its user-friendly and intuitive platform, making it easier and more efficient for borrowers to secure debt financing and for investors to facilitate P2P lending in the real estate industry.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Any legal entity based in Switzerland that has a UID entry and a professional treasury department. That includes all insurers, pension funds and banks, professional asset managers and family offices as well as public corporations.', 'loanboox', '2023-08-08 09:32:55', '2023-08-08 09:32:55'),
(190, '3circlefunding.ch', '/platformLogo/3circlefunding.ch.png', '[\"Switzerland\"]', '[\"P2P lending\"]', '[\"SME\"]', '2015', 'N/A', '[\"Dutch\",\"English\"]', NULL, 'https://www.3circlefunding.ch/', '1 EUR', '3.5-10%', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', '3circlefunding.ch is a crowdfunding platform based in Switzerland that primarily focuses on peer-to-peer lending in the small and medium enterprise (SME) industry. Established in 2015, 3circlefunding aims to provide borrowers and lenders with more flexibility and autonomy over their loans.\n\nThe platform operates in two languages, Dutch and English, making it accessible to a wider range of investors. With a minimum investment of just 1 EUR, it offers a low entry barrier for individuals who are interested in investing in SMEs.\n\nOne of the unique features of 3circlefunding is that it allows borrowers to determine the interest rates for their loans. This empowers borrowers and enables them to find more favorable financing terms. Additionally, investors have the opportunity to sell loan parts in the secondary market, providing them with increased liquidity and potential for higher returns.\n\nThe platform boasts a diverse range of investment opportunities, with advertised returns ranging from 3.5% to 10%. This wide range ensures that investors can select projects that align with their risk appetite and investment goals.\n\nBoth personal and corporate investors can take advantage of 3circlefunding\'s offerings, enhancing its appeal to a broad investor base. The platform\'s user-friendly website, located at https://www.3circlefunding.ch/, provides a convenient and streamlined experience for users to access information and participate in investment activities.\n\nIn summary, 3circlefunding.ch is a pioneering crowdfunding platform in Switzerland that facilitates P2P lending in the SME sector. Through its borrower-set interest rates and secondary market for loan parts, it empowers borrowers and offers increased flexibility to investors. With its low minimum investment requirement and attractive advertised returns, the platform presents an appealing opportunity for both personal and corporate investors.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Personal, Corporate', '3circlefunding.ch', '2023-08-08 09:32:55', '2023-08-08 09:32:55');
