(197, 'Kocoriko', '/platformLogo/Kocoriko.png', '[\"France\"]', '[\"Reward\"]', '[\"Social cause\"]', '2015', '15005442', '[\"French\",\"English\"]', NULL, 'https://www.kocoriko.fr/', '1€', 'N/A', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Kocoriko is a French-based crowdfunding platform that was founded in 2015. It is the first of its kind to focus specifically on projects in the Auvergne Rhône Alpes region. The platform operates on a reward-based investment model, where individuals and corporations can contribute to projects and receive various rewards in return.\n\nThe main industry targeted by Kocoriko is social causes, with a specific emphasis on projects that have an economic, cultural, innovative, or solidarity dimension. This showcases the platform\'s commitment to supporting initiatives that have a positive impact on society.\n\nKocoriko offers a user-friendly experience by providing its services in French and English, making it accessible to a wider audience. The platform\'s website, https://www.kocoriko.fr/, provides all the necessary information for potential investors and project creators.\n\nOne notable aspect of Kocoriko is that there is no advertised return for investments. Instead, investors receive rewards based on their contribution to a particular project. This approach allows individuals to support causes they care about while receiving unique benefits in return.\n\nKocoriko accepts investments starting from a minimum of 1 unit of currency, making it accessible to anyone interested in supporting projects on the platform. Both personal and corporate investors are welcomed on Kocoriko, ensuring a diverse range of projects to support.\n\nIn summary, Kocoriko is a pioneering crowdfunding platform based in France that focuses on projects in the Auvergne Rhône Alpes region. With a commitment to social causes and an inclusive approach to investment, Kocoriko provides a platform for individuals and corporations to support innovative and impactful projects.', 0,