(266, 'Brocc', '/platformLogo/Brocc.png', '[\"Sweden\"]', '[\"P2P lending\"]', '[\"Personal loans\"]', '2014', NULL, '[\"Swedish\"]', NULL, 'https://brocc.se/', '10,000 EUR', 'N/A', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Brocc is a crowdfunding platform based in Sweden that specializes in peer-to-peer lending. Founded in 2014, the platform serves as a marketplace where private individuals can exchange financial services. Brocc\'s primary focus is on providing personal loans to individuals.\n\nThe platform aims to challenge the traditional financial market and offer better terms for financial services. Since its establishment in 2014, Brocc has been committed to providing a user-friendly and efficient platform for peer-to-peer lending, catering to the needs of both borrowers and lenders.\n\nAs a P2P lending platform, Brocc allows personal and corporate investors to participate in the lending process. The platform connects borrowers with investors, cutting out the middleman associated with traditional lending institutions. This direct approach enables investors to receive better returns on their investment while borrowers benefit from more favorable loan terms.\n\nBrocc\'s website, available in Swedish, provides information on various investment opportunities and procedures. The minimum investment amount on the platform is 10,000 EUR, ensuring that both small and large investors can participate. However, the exact advertised return on investment is not stated on the website.\n\nOverall, Brocc strives to revolutionize the financial industry in Sweden by providing a transparent and accessible platform for peer-to-peer lending.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Personal, Corporate', 'brocc', '2023-08-08 09:32:55', '2023-08-08 09:32:55'),
