(350, 'Coates Finance', '/platformLogo/Coates Finance.png', '[\"United Kingdom\"]', '[\"Equity\",\"P2P lending\"]', '[\"SME\"]', '2013', '807354', '[\"English\"]', NULL, 'https://www.coatesfinance.com/', '1 EUR', 'N/A', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Coates Finance is a crowdfunding platform based in York, United Kingdom. It was founded in 2013 and primarily operates in the SME (small and medium-sized enterprises) industry. The platform offers two types of investments: equity and peer-to-peer lending. \n\nCoates Finance focuses on providing business finance solutions that enable access to additional sources of cash. Their asset finance services help businesses secure the funding they need to expand or meet short-term financial requirements. \n\nInvestors on the platform can choose between equity investments or P2P lending opportunities. With equity investments, individuals have the opportunity to become shareholders in promising SMEs that are seeking funding. P2P lending allows investors to lend money to small businesses and earn interest on their investment.\n\nThe platform is available to investors from around the world, with English being the primary language used on the website. Coates Finance has a minimum investment requirement of 1 EUR, making it accessible to a wide range of potential investors.\n\nWhile the exact returns on investments are not explicitly advertised, investors can expect to earn interest on P2P loans or potentially benefit from the growth of the businesses they invest in through equity. The website provides more information on the investment opportunities and allows potential investors to sign up and get started.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, 'coatesfinance', '2023-08-08 09:32:55', '2023-08-08 09:32:55'),
(351, 'Money&Co', '/platformLogo/Money&Co.png', '[\"United Kingdom\"]', '[\"P2P lending\"]', '[\"SME\"]', '2013', '8561817', '[\"English\"]', NULL, 'https://moneyandco.com/', '100 GBP', '8%', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Money&Co is a crowdfunding platform based in the United Kingdom that specializes in P2P lending. Founded in 2013, their primary focus is on providing investment opportunities for small and medium-sized enterprises (SMEs). The platform operates in English and is accessible through their website at https://moneyandco.com/.\n\nMoney&Co aims to connect investors who are seeking a more competitive rate of interest on their funds with businesses that are in need of financial support. This P2B (peer-to-business) crowdfunding model allows individuals to lend money directly to SMEs, cutting out traditional financial intermediaries. By doing so, both parties benefit as investors can earn potentially higher returns while businesses gain access to the funds they require.\n\nTo start investing on Money&Co, the platform requires a minimum investment of £100. The advertised return on investments is 0.08, indicating a potential interest rate or ROI for lenders. This return rate may vary depending on individual investments and the performance of the businesses funded.\n\nMoney&Co offers a unique investment opportunity for individuals who seek to support SMEs and potentially earn attractive returns on their investment. By bypassing traditional financial institutions and connecting lenders directly with businesses, the platform provides a more streamlined and accessible approach to crowdfunding in the United Kingdom.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL, 'money&co', '2023-08-08 09:32:55', '2023-08-08 09:32:55'),
(352, 'Crowdestates', '/platformLogo/Crowdestates.png', '[\"United Kingdom\"]', '[\"P2P lending\"]', '[\"Real estate\"]', '2013', '8728808', '[\"English\"]', NULL, 'https://crowdestates.com/', '10 GBP', 'N/A', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Anyone can invest in Crowdestates as long as they are at least 18 years old, a resident of the United Kingdom, and have a valid UK bank account. The platform offers P2P lending opportunities in the real estate industry, allowing investors to lend money directly to community-led development projects with a social impact. \n\nCrowdestates was founded in 2013 and is based in the United Kingdom. The platform is available in English, making it accessible to a wide audience. The website, https://crowdestates.com/, provides all the necessary information and tools for investors to browse and select investment opportunities.\n\nThe minimum investment required on Crowdestates is £10, making it a relatively affordable option for potential investors. However, the advertised return on investment is not provided, so investors need to further research the potential profitability of the platform.\n\nOverall, Crowdestates aims to help communities by providing them with development finance for social impact projects, while also offering investors the opportunity to access real estate investments in the UK. With its focus on social impact and community involvement, Crowdestates offers a unique approach to P2P lending in the real estate industry.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, 'crowdestates', '2023-08-08 09:32:55', '2023-08-08 09:32:55'),
(353, 'Relendex', '/platformLogo/Relendex.png', '[\"United Kingdom\"]', '[\"P2P lending\"]', '[\"Real estate\"]', '2013', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://www.relendex.com/', '500 GBP', 'N/A', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Relendex is a crowdfunding platform based in the United Kingdom that specializes in peer-to-peer (P2P) lending in the real estate industry. It was founded in 2013 with the aim of connecting lenders with creditworthy borrowers, providing mutually beneficial interest rates to both parties. \n\nBy focusing on commercial real estate lending, Relendex offers investors the opportunity to diversify their portfolios and participate in the lucrative property market. The platform meticulously vets all potential borrowers to ensure their creditworthiness and the security of the investments.\n\nRelendex\'s website, available at https://www.relendex.com/, serves as a user-friendly platform where lenders can make investments starting from a minimum of 500 GBP. While the exact advertised return is not specified, investors can expect attractive interest rates, taking advantage of the potential profitability that the real estate market offers.\n\nOne of the key strengths of Relendex is its commitment to security. All funds lent through the platform are secured on United Kingdom properties, providing an additional layer of protection for investors. This reassurance, along with the platform\'s professional vetting process, attracts both individual and institutional investors looking for reliable opportunities in the real estate lending space.\n\nRelendex\'s P2P lending platform is open to various types of investors, offering access to commercial real estate opportunities that were traditionally limited to a select few. With a solid track record since its establishment in 2013, Relendex remains a reputable and promising option for those seeking to invest in the booming real estate market in the United Kingdom.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, 'relendex', '2023-08-08 09:32:55