(356, 'Lymo', '/platformLogo/Lymo.png', '[\"France\"]', '[\"Equity\"]', '[\"Real estate\"]', '2013', '15004746', '[\"French\"]', NULL, 'https://lymo.fr/', '1,000 EUR', '8-12%', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Lymo is a prominent crowdfunding platform based in France that specializes in real estate investments. Established in 2013, Lymo has been at the forefront of real estate crowdfunding in the country. The platform primarily focuses on small-scale residential real estate projects that are known for their limited number of neighbors, low condominium fees, and central locations.\n\nLymo offers an equity investment model where individuals can invest in these real estate projects and become part owners. The platform facilitates investments in various residential properties, enabling investors to diversify their portfolio by participating in different projects. Investors on Lymo can expect attractive returns, as the platform advertises a potential return ranging from 8% to 12%.\n\nAs a French-based platform, Lymo operates primarily in the French language. Its user-friendly website provides comprehensive information about the available investment opportunities, including details on the properties and projected returns. The minimum investment amount required to participate on Lymo is 1,000 EUR, allowing a wide range of investors to take part in these projects.\n\nLymo\'s focus on small-scale residential real estate projects sets it apart from other crowdfunding platforms in the country. By targeting properties with low condominium fees and a limited number of neighbors, Lymo appeals to investors seeking a quieter and more exclusive investment experience. With its strong track record and unique investment offerings, Lymo offers a promising avenue for individuals looking to invest in the French real estate market.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, 'lymo', '2023-08-08 09:32:55', '2023-08-08 09:32:55');
