(359, 'Finple', '/platformLogo/Finple.png', '[\"France\"]', '[\"Equity\",\"P2P lending\"]', '[\"SME\"]', '2013', '15004344', '[\"French\"]', NULL, 'https://finple.com/', '1,000 EUR', '9,5%', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Anyone can invest in Finple as long as they meet the minimum investment requirement of 1,000 EUR. The platform primarily focuses on equity-based investment and peer-to-peer (P2P) lending, allowing investors to financially support small and medium-sized enterprises (SMEs) in France.\n\nFounded in 2013 and headquartered in France, Finple provides an online platform for individuals to invest in SMEs and receive potential returns. The platform is operated in the French language, catering to a predominantly French-speaking audience.\n\nFinple aims to provide a unique value proposition by combining the efficiency and convenience of a digital platform with the expertise and guidance of passionate entrepreneurship guides. These guides assist investors and entrepreneurs in navigating their crowdfunding journey, offering insights and support throughout the process.\n\nThe minimum investment requirement of 1,000 EUR enables a wide range of individuals to participate and contribute to the growth of SMEs. The advertised return on investments is 0.095, indicating the potential profitability for investors.\n\nOverall, Finple offers a platform that connects investors with entrepreneurs, allowing them to support and contribute to the success of SMEs in France. Its combination of digital features and personalized guidance sets it apart in the crowdfunding landscape, providing a unique experience for both investors and entrepreneurs.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL, 'finple', '2023-08-08 09:32:55', '2023-08-08 09:32:55'),
(360, 'Toborrow', '/platformLogo/Toborrow.png', '[\"Sweden\"]', '[\"P2P lending\"]', '[\"SME\"]', '2013', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://www.toborrow.com/', '100 EUR', 'N/A', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Anyone can invest on the Toborrow crowdfunding platform, regardless of their geographic location. However, the platform is primarily targeted towards individuals and businesses in Sweden. \n\nToborrow focuses on Peer-to-Peer (P2P) lending, connecting investors with small and medium-sized enterprises (SMEs) in need of funding. This alternative form of investment allows individuals to directly lend money to SMEs, bypassing traditional financial institutions such as banks.\n\nFounded in 2013, Toborrow has established itself as a reliable and reputable platform for borrowers and lenders. The platform is entirely digital, offering a user-friendly and secure loan process. By eliminating the bureaucratic hurdles associated with traditional banks, Toborrow delivers a streamlined experience to both investors and borrowers.\n\nWhile the exact advertised return on investment is not mentioned, investors have the opportunity to earn interest on the loans they provide to SMEs. To encourage participation, Toborrow has set a minimum investment requirement of 100 EUR, making it accessible to a wide range of investors.\n\nToborrow\'s mission is to facilitate growth by connecting investors and borrowers who would otherwise remain unknown to each other, creating mutual benefits for both parties. With its inclusive approach and emphasis on SMEs, Toborrow plays a vital role in supporting the growth of the Swedish economy. Interested parties can find more information and access the platform through the Toborrow website at https://www.toborrow.com/.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, 'toborrow', '2023-08-08 09:32:55', '2023-08-08 09:32:55'),
(361, 'Grow.ly', '/platformLogo/Grow.ly.png', '[\"Spain\"]', '[\"P2P lending\"]', '[\"SME\"]', '2013', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://www.grow.ly/', '50 EUR', 'N/A', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', '32,222,220 EUR', '11 months', 'Any individual or legal entity can invest in Grow.ly as long as they comply with the platform\'s requirements. The platform allows investors to lend directly to small and medium-sized enterprises (SMEs) in Spain. Grow.ly operates based on peer-to-peer (P2P) lending, where multiple individuals contribute funds to finance the growth projects of these SMEs.\n\nFounded in 2013, Grow.ly is a registered Participatory Financing Platform with the CNMV (National Securities Market Commission), ensuring compliance with regulatory standards and providing a level of trust and security to investors. \n\nGrow.ly is primarily focused on supporting the heart of the economy, which comprises small and medium-sized businesses. By providing them with the necessary funding, the platform actively collaborates in their development, strengthening the overall economic landscape in Spain.\n\nWith a minimum investment of 50 EUR, Grow.ly offers an accessible entry point for investors interested in participating in P2P lending and supporting local businesses. Although the platform does not specify an advertised return, investors can expect potential returns based on the interest rates negotiated with the SME borrowers.\n\nDespite the limited provided information, Grow.ly appears to be a promising crowdfunding platform that brings together investors and SMEs in Spain, fostering economic growth and development. More details about the platform, such as available languages, are not explicitly mentioned but can be explored on their website.', 1, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, NULL, 'grow.ly', '2023-08-08 09:32:55', '2023-08-08 09:32:55'),
