(381, 'Crowdahouse', '/platformLogo/Crowdahouse.png', '[\"United Kingdom\"]', '[\"P2P lending\"]', '[\"Real estate\"]', '2012', 'ZA105392', '[\"English\"]', NULL, 'http://crowdahouse.com/', '500 EUR', '10%', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Crowdahouse is a crowdfunding platform based in the United Kingdom that offers P2P lending services in the real estate industry. Established in 2012, the platform operates primarily in English and provides an opportunity for individuals to invest in property projects. The minimum investment required to participate on Crowdahouse is 500 EUR.\n\nThe platform focuses on lending to property professionals rather than individuals, which helps mitigate risk. All loans are secured against property, offering an additional layer of security for investors. With Crowdahouse, investors have the chance to earn a specified return on their investment, which is advertised at 0.1%.\n\nCrowdahouse\'s main function is to connect investors with property professionals seeking funding for their projects. By lending to these professionals, individuals can support various real estate ventures while potentially earning a return on their investment.\n\nOperating exclusively in the United Kingdom, Crowdahouse is a reliable platform for those interested in investing in the real estate market. With its easy-to-use website, investors can quickly navigate through available projects and make informed decisions regarding their investments.\n\nOverall, Crowdahouse provides an accessible and secure platform for individuals looking to engage in P2P lending within the real estate industry, offering opportunities for both investment growth and financial support for property professionals.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL, 'crowdahouse', '2023-08-08 09:32:56', '2023-08-08 09:32:56'),
(382, 'FundingSecure', '/platformLogo/FundingSecure.png', '[\"United Kingdom\"]', '[\"P2P lending\"]', '[\"Real estate\"]', '2012', '8120200', '[\"English\"]', NULL, 'https://www.fundingsecure.com/', '25 GBP', 'Up to 13%', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Anyone aged 18 or over, with a UK bank account and a valid ID. FundingSecure, founded in 2012 in the United Kingdom, is a crowdfunding platform that focuses on peer-to-peer lending in the real estate industry. The platform offers tax-efficient Innovative ISA programs and carefully selected lending opportunities. \n\nFundingSecure prides itself on its rigorous selection and detailed appraisal process for investment opportunities, ensuring that they are robustly structured and professionally managed. This gives investors confidence in the platform and the projects they choose to invest in. \n\nInvestors on FundingSecure can join with a minimum investment of just 25 GBP, making it accessible to a wide range of individuals. The platform offers an advertised return of up to 13%, providing the potential for attractive earnings on investments.\n\nFundingSecure operates primarily in English, making it easily accessible to investors in the United Kingdom and other English-speaking countries. Their website, https://www.fundingsecure.com/, serves as a hub for investors to browse available opportunities, access information, and make investments.\n\nTo become an investor on FundingSecure, individuals must be at least 18 years old, have a UK bank account, and possess a valid identification document. With these requirements, FundingSecure offers a convenient opportunity for investors to engage in peer-to-peer lending and build their portfolio in the real estate industry.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL, 'fundingsecure', '2023-08-08 09:32:56', '2023-08-08 09:32:56'),
(383, 'Backtowork24', '/platformLogo/Backtowork24.png', '[\"Italy\"]', '[\"Equity\"]', '[\"Real estate\",\"SME\"]', '2012', '19102', '[\"Italian\"]', NULL, 'https://www.backtowork24.com/', '500 EUR', 'N/A', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Backtowork24 is an equity crowdfunding platform based in Italy that was founded in 2012. It primarily focuses on investments in startups, small and medium-sized enterprises (SMEs), and real estate projects. The platform operates exclusively in Italian and offers opportunities for both private and professional investors.\n\nAs an equity crowdfunding platform, Backtowork24 allows individuals to invest in businesses and real estate ventures in exchange for ownership stakes or shares in the projects. This investment type offers the potential for financial returns based on the success of the ventures.\n\nBacktowork24 sets a minimum investment requirement of 500 EUR, making it accessible to a wide range of investors. However, the advertised return on these investments is not specified on the platform.\n\nWith its focus on startups, SMEs, and real estate, Backtowork24 provides an opportunity for investors to support and benefit from the growth and success of these sectors in Italy. By connecting investors with promising projects, the platform facilitates the flow of capital and contributes to the development of the Italian economy.\n\nOverall, Backtowork24 is a leading equity crowdfunding platform in Italy that promotes investment in startups, SMEs, and real estate projects, offering individuals the chance to invest and potentially gain ownership stakes in these ventures.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL, 'backtowork24', '2023-08-08 09:32:56', '2023-08-08 09:32:56'),
(384, 'Lending Works', '/platformLogo/Lending Works.png', '[\"United Kingdom\"]', '[\"P2P lending\"]', '[\"SME\"]', '2012', '723151', '[\"English\"]', NULL, 'https://www.lendingworks.co.uk/', '10 EUR', '4.50%', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Lending Works is a crowdfunding platform based in the United Kingdom that focuses on peer-to-peer lending. Established in 2012, the platform specializes in providing unsecured personal loans to borrowers within the United Kingdom. The platform aims to minimize risk by employing a diversification strategy and utilizing the \'Lending Works Shield,\' a provision fund.\n\nThe investment type offered through Lending Works is peer-to-peer lending, which means that individual investors can directly lend money to borrowers. This creates an opportunity for investors to earn attractive returns on their investments, with an advertised return rate of 4.50%.\n\nLending Works primarily targets the SME (Small and Medium Enterprises) industry in the United Kingdom, offering unsecured personal loans to support business growth and investment. This sector is known for its economic significance and entrepreneurial potential, making it an attractive investment opportunity for individuals.\n\nWith a minimum investment requirement of 10 EUR, Lending Works strives to make investing accessible to a wide range of individuals. The platform is user-friendly and available in English, ensuring ease of use for investors.\n\nOverall, Lending Works provides a crowdfunding platform for investors seeking opportunities in peer-to-peer lending within the SME industry in the United Kingdom. Its focus on risk mitigation, diversification, and provision fund enables investors to support individual borrowers while potentially earning attractive returns on their investments.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL, 'lendingworks', '2023-08-08 09:32:56', '2023-08-08 09:32:56');
