(419, 'Windcentrale', '/platformLogo/Windcentrale.png', '[\"Netherlands\"]', '[\"Equity\"]', '[\"Green energy\"]', '2010', NULL, '[\"Dutch\"]', NULL, 'https://www.windcentrale.nl/', '1 EUR', '6-7%', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Anyone can invest in Windcentrale, regardless of their background or profession. The platform is open to individuals who are interested in supporting green energy and want to become co-owners of a windmill. It provides an opportunity for people to actively participate in the generation of clean, renewable energy.\n\nAs an equity crowdfunding platform, Windcentrale offers the chance to invest in green energy projects in the Netherlands. Investors can purchase shares in windmills, becoming co-owners and receiving a proportionate share of the energy produced by these windmills. This allows individuals to benefit financially from the energy generated by the windmills they have invested in.\n\nThe Windcentrale was founded in 2010 and has since become a prominent player in the green energy industry. It aims to accelerate the transition to sustainable energy in the Netherlands by enabling broad participation in wind energy projects. The platform primarily operates in Dutch and offers a minimum investment of just 1 EUR, making it accessible to a wide range of individuals.\n\nOne of the key advantages of investing through Windcentrale is the potential return on investment. The platform advertises a return of 6-7%, which can be a lucrative opportunity for investors looking for sustainable and profitable investments.\n\nWith its focus on green energy and commitment to democratizing access to wind energy, Windcentrale is playing a vital role in promoting sustainability and renewable energy generation in the Netherlands.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, 'windcentrale', '2023-08-08 09:32:56', '2023-08-08 09:32:56'),
