(462, 'JustGiving', '/platformLogo/JustGiving.png', '[\"United Kingdom\"]', '[\"Donation\"]', '[\"Social cause\"]', '2001', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://www.justgiving.com/', '1 EUR', 'N/A', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'JustGiving is a crowdfunding platform based in the United Kingdom, primarily focused on social causes. Founded in 2001, it is considered the world\'s most trusted online giving platform. Its main objective is to connect global causes with individuals who are passionate about making a difference.\n\nJustGiving operates through a donation-based investment model, allowing users to contribute to various social causes. Unlike traditional investment platforms, JustGiving does not offer any advertised return on investment. Instead, it aims to create a platform where individuals can donate as little as 1 EUR to support causes they believe in.\n\nThe crowdfunding platform is available for individuals and organizations from around the world. Its website, located at https://www.justgiving.com/, provides a user-friendly interface and allows users to easily explore and support causes of their choice.\n\nOverall, JustGiving\'s mission is to foster a sense of connectedness between global causes and people who genuinely care about making a positive impact in their communities and beyond. Through its platform, individuals can contribute to causes they are passionate about, regardless of their financial capacity.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, 'justgiving', '2023-08-08 09:32:56', '2023-08-08 09:32:56'),
