(464, 'Privanet', '/platformLogo/Privanet.png', '[\"Finland\"]', '[\"Equity\",\"P2P lending\"]', '[\"Real estate\"]', '2000', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://privanet.fi/premarket/', '100,000 EUR', 'N/A', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Privanet is a leading crowdfunding platform in Finland that specializes in equity and P2P lending investments in the real estate industry. Established in 2000, Privanet Securities Ltd\'s marketplace is well-known and has gained a strong reputation in the market for its expertise in unlisted securities.\n\nThe platform offers opportunities for individuals or businesses to invest in unlisted companies in Finland, providing a range of funding options. While the minimum investment required is 100,000 EUR, Privanet offers investors the chance to diversify their portfolio and participate in the real estate market.\n\nAlthough the platform does not advertise specific returns, it prides itself on its extensive brokerage experience and knowledge of unlisted companies in Finland. This provides investors with a level of confidence and trust in their investments.\n\nPrivanet\'s website, available at https://privanet.fi/premarket/, serves as a hub for potential investors to explore investment opportunities and access further information. The platform attracts individuals, businesses, and institutions interested in investing in the Finnish real estate sector.\n\nWith its long-standing presence in the market, Privanet has positioned itself as a reputable crowdfunding platform in Finland and continues to provide investment opportunities to interested parties.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, 'privanet', '2023-08-08 09:32:56', '2023-08-08 09:32:56'),
(465, 'Lendwithcare', '/platformLogo/Lendwithcare.png', '[\"United Kingdom\"]', '[\"P2P lending\"]', '[\"SME\"]', '1985', '292506', '[\"English\"]', NULL, 'https://lendwithcare.org/', '15 GBP', 'N/A', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Lendwithcare is a crowdfunding platform based in the United Kingdom. Founded in 1985, it operates as a peer-to-peer lending platform aimed at helping small and medium-sized enterprises (SMEs) in low-income countries. Lendwithcare provides a way for individuals and corporations to invest in small businesses in these countries and contribute to poverty alleviation.\n\nThe platform allows investors to lend as little as £15 to fund a small business of their choice. The funds provided are aimed at supporting entrepreneurs in these countries, enabling them to work their way out of poverty with dignity. Once the invested money is repaid, investors have the option to reinvest it in other businesses or withdraw the funds.\n\nLendwithcare\'s website is available in English, making it accessible to a wide range of potential investors. However, the platform does not provide specific details regarding the advertised return on investment or the expected rates of return for lenders.\n\nLendwithcare caters to both personal and corporate investors. This inclusivity allows individuals and businesses to contribute to the economic growth and development of SMEs in low-income countries. By providing financial support, Lendwithcare aims to empower entrepreneurs and stimulate sustainable business growth, ultimately helping people lift themselves out of poverty.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Personal, Corporate', 'lendwithcare', '2023-08-08 09:32:56', '2023-08-08 09:32:56'),
(466, 'OZÉ', '/platformLogo/OZÉ.png', '[\"France\"]', '[\"Donation\"]', '[\"SME\"]', '1972', '17004579', '[\"French\"]', NULL, 'https://www.ozecontribuer-manche.fr/fr', '1€', 'N/A', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'OZÉ Contribute is a crowdfunding platform based in France that facilitates donations for small and medium-sized enterprises (SMEs). Founded in 1972, OZÉ Contribute aims to connect project leaders and contributors, providing a platform for individuals and businesses to support local initiatives. The platform is primarily in French, catering to a French-speaking audience.\n\nOZÉ Contribute allows project leaders to showcase their projects, seek financial assistance, and communicate with potential supporters. Whether individuals have a project in their community that requires a financial boost or simply want to participate in local initiatives, OZÉ Contribute provides a platform for individuals and businesses to contribute and make a difference.\n\nThe minimum investment amount on OZÉ Contribute is 1 currency unit, allowing anyone to contribute based on their financial capabilities. While the platform advertises no specific return on investment, supporters can expect the satisfaction of helping local projects and contributing to their community\'s growth.\n\nBoth personal and corporate investors can participate on OZÉ Contribute, expanding the potential reach and impact of the platform. Any individual or business interested in supporting local initiatives or seeking financial assistance for their own projects can utilize OZÉ Contribute as a crowdfunding platform of choice.\n\nTo access OZÉ Contribute and explore the various projects available for support or funding, interested individuals and businesses can visit their website at https://www.ozecontribuer-manche.fr/fr.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Personal, Corporate', 'ozé', '2023-08-08 09:32:56', '2023-08-08 09:32:56'),
(467, 'Isicrowd', '/platformLogo/Isicrowd.png', '[\"Italy\"]', '[\"Debt\"]', '[\"Real estate\"]', '2020', 'N/A', '[\"Italian\"]', NULL, 'https://isicrowd.it/?tclid=102f097d86bc04e476536bff60757f%7C1255%7C%7C%7C%7C%7C%7C%7C', '50 EUR', '11%', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', '699,000 EUR', 'N/A', 'Isicrowd is a crowdfunding platform based in Italy that specializes in debt investment within the real estate industry. Founded in 2020, Isicrowd aims to expand its services in the tourism sector. As the first crowdfunding platform in southern Italy, it has positioned itself as a leader in the region.\n\nThe platform operates primarily in the Italian language, catering to the local market. Its website, available at https://isicrowd.it, provides detailed information for potential investors. The minimum investment required is 50 EUR, allowing individuals with varying budgets to participate.\n\nIsicrowd offers an advertised return rate of 0.11, which may attract investors seeking relatively stable and predictable returns. This makes it an attractive option for both private and institutional investors looking to diversify their portfolios.\n\nBy focusing on debt investment in real estate, Isicrowd capitalizes on the potential profitability of this booming industry. Additionally, their intention to expand into the tourism field demonstrates their commitment to adapting to market trends and catering to evolving investor demands.\n\nOverall, Isicrowd presents an intriguing crowdfunding opportunity for those interested in real estate debt investment in Italy. Its status as the first platform of its kind in southern Italy and its dedication to expanding its services indicate a promising future for the company.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Private and institutional investors are welcome.', 'isicrowd', '2023-08-08 09:32:56', '2023-08-08 09:32:56'),
