(568, 'Invesdor', '/platformLogo/Invesdor.png', '[\"Austria\",\"Finland\",\"Sweden\"]', '[\"Equity\",\"Debt\"]', '[\"Real estate\"]', '2012', 'FIVA 39/02.02.00/2014', '[\"English\",\"German\",\"Finnish\"]', NULL, 'https://www.invesdor.com/', '500 EUR', '6.49%', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Invesdor is an equity-based crowdfunding platform that operates in Austria, Finland, and Sweden. Founded in 2012 and headquartered in Helsinki, Finland, Invesdor is known as the first equity-based crowdfunding service in Northern Europe. The platform facilitates investments in the real estate industry.\n\nWith a user-friendly website available in English, German, and Finnish, Invesdor welcomes investors from diverse linguistic backgrounds, ensuring easy access and communication. The minimum investment required on the platform is 500 EUR, making it accessible to a wide range of investors.\n\nInvesdor provides an advertised return of 6.49%, attracting individuals looking for investment opportunities in the real estate sector. The platform offers two types of investment options: equity and debt. This allows investors to choose the type of investment that suits their preferences and risk appetite.\n\nFunctioning as a matching service, Invesdor connects investors interested in real estate projects with developers and companies seeking funding. By providing a transparent and secure platform, Invesdor enables individuals to participate in real estate investments without the need for large amounts of capital or prior experience in the industry.\n\nIn summary, Invesdor is an established crowdfunding platform that has revolutionized the equity-based crowdfunding scene in Northern Europe. With a focus on real estate investments, multilingual support, and a low minimum investment requirement, Invesdor provides a unique opportunity for investors to diversify their portfolios and potentially earn attractive returns.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'N/A', 'invesdor', '2023-08-08 09:32:56', '2023-08-08