(569, 'Booomerang.dk', '/platformLogo/Booomerang.dk.png', '[\"Denmark\"]', '[\"Reward\"]', '[\"Social cause\"]', '2011', '36413654', '[\"Danish\"]', NULL, 'https://booomerang.dk/', '1 EUR', 'N/A', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Booomerang.dk is Denmark\'s leading reward-based crowdfunding platform, established in 2011. It operates as a means for individuals and businesses to support social causes and innovative projects. With a strong focus on encouraging positive changes in society, Booomerang.dk provides a platform for various types of initiatives to access funding.\n\nThe platform supports projects from individuals or organizations that aim to make a social impact. Booomerang.dk is committed to fostering a community of contributors who share the vision of creating a better future. Through crowdfunding, it allows these projects to gain financial support from a wide range of backers.\n\nAlthough primarily operating in Danish, Booomerang.dk is easily accessible for users in Denmark and beyond. The website, https://booomerang.dk/, acts as a hub for crowdfunding campaigns, providing information and updates about ongoing and upcoming projects.\n\nOne key feature of Booomerang.dk is its accessibility, as it allows investments starting from just 1 EUR. While the platform does not advertise a specific return on investment, it offers a sense of fulfillment by allowing individuals and organizations to contribute to projects that can lead to positive social change.\n\nFurthermore, Booomerang.dk is expanding its services beyond reward-based crowdfunding. As of August 2022, the platform will also offer crowdfunding loans (crowdlending), providing additional financial opportunities for projects looking for alternative funding options.\n\nBooomerang.dk welcomes both personal and corporate investors, allowing a diverse range of individuals and businesses to contribute. By providing a platform for social causes and innovative projects, Booomerang.dk contributes to the growth and advancement of Danish society.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Personal, Corporate', 'booomerang.dk', '2023-08-08 09:32:56', '2023-08-08 09:32:56'),
(570, 'Dozen', '/platformLogo/Dozen.png', '[\"Spain\"]', '[\"Equity\"]', '[\"Startups\"]', '2011', 'N/A', '[\"English\",\"Spanish\"]', NULL, 'https://dozeninvestments.com/', '1 EUR', 'N/A', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Dozen is a crowdfunding platform based in Spain that focuses on equity investments in startup companies. Founded in 2011, Dozen aims to connect investors with high-growth potential projects led by ambitious and talented teams. The platform\'s mission is to profitably channel a portion of their investors\' savings towards these projects in order to generate a productive economy, employment, and value for society.\n\nDozen caters to both personal and corporate investors, providing an opportunity for individuals and businesses to invest in startups and contribute to their growth. With a minimum investment of just 1 EUR, Dozen ensures that even small investors can participate in these opportunities.\n\nThe platform operates in both English and Spanish, allowing investors from different countries and backgrounds to easily access and engage with the investment opportunities available. The company\'s website, https://dozeninvestments.com/, serves as a hub for investors to learn more about the projects, explore potential investment options, and connect with the entrepreneurial teams seeking funding.\n\nAlthough the specific advertised return is not mentioned, the emphasis on high growth potential suggests that investors have the opportunity to earn significant returns on their investments. By supporting startups, Dozen not only provides an opportunity for financial gains but also aims to contribute to the overall development of a vibrant and productive startup ecosystem in Spain and beyond.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Personal, Cooperate', 'dozen', '2023-08-08 09:32:56', '2023-08-08 09:32:56'),
(571, 'Spreds', '/platformLogo/Spreds.png', '[\"Belgium\"]', '[\"Equity\"]', '[\"Real estate\",\"Startups\",\"SME\",\"Green energy\",\"Health & Science\"]', '2011', '0837.496.614', '[\"EN\",\"NL\",\"FR\"]', NULL, 'https://www.spreds.com/en', '100 EUR', 'N/A', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Spreds is a crowdfunding platform based in Belgium, founded in 2011. It offers investment opportunities in various industries including real estate, startups, SMEs, green energy, and health & science. The platform supports both equity and loan crowdfunding campaigns, specifically targeting projects aiming to raise funds between €50,000 and €1,000,000.\n\nSpreds works by connecting campaigns with multiple types of investors such as Business Angels (BAs), Venture Capitalists (VCs), Family Offices, Funds, and others. Private individuals as well as companies are eligible to invest on the platform. \n\nThe platform supports three languages: English, Dutch, and French, making it accessible to a wide range of users. With a minimum investment requirement of €100, Spreds aims to make crowdfunding accessible to a diverse investor base.\n\nUnfortunately, the advertised return on investments is not specified, so potential investors might need to review individual campaign opportunities to understand the potential returns. \n\nOverall, Spreds.com provides a platform for individuals and companies in Belgium to invest in a range of industries, supporting both equity and loan crowdfunding campaigns. With its diverse investor network, it aims to facilitate fundraising for campaigns looking for larger funding amounts.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Private individuals, companies.', 'spreds', '2023-08-08 09:32:56', '2023-08-08 09:32:56'),
(572, 'CapitalStackers', '/platformLogo/CapitalStackers.png', '[\"United Kingdom\"]', '[\"P2P lending\"]', '[\"Real estate\"]', '2010', 'N/A', '[\"English\"]', NULL, 'https://www.capitalstackers.com/', '5,000 GBP', 'N/A', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'CapitalStackers is a crowdfunding platform based in the United Kingdom that specializes in P2P lending within the real estate industry. Founded in 2010, the platform is primarily focused on enabling smaller investors to participate in property development alongside banks. \n\nOn the CapitalStackers platform, investors have the opportunity to invest in property development projects and earn returns through P2P lending. The platform is designed to provide a secure and hassle-free way for individuals and corporations to invest in real estate. \n\nThe website, available in English, offers detailed information about the investment opportunities available, as well as the ability to create an account and start investing. The minimum investment required to participate is £5,000, making it accessible to a range of investors.\n\nWhile the specific advertised return is not provided, the platform boasts a team of seasoned professionals with a wealth of experience in banking and real estate. This expertise ensures that investors can have confidence in the platform\'s ability to achieve successful investment outcomes.\n\nBoth personal and corporate investors are eligible to participate on CapitalStackers, providing an opportunity for various types of investors to diversify their portfolios and potentially benefit from the returns generated by real estate development projects.\n\nIn summary, CapitalStackers offers a peer-to-peer lending platform for real estate investment, allowing smaller investors to participate alongside traditional banks. With a minimum investment of £5,000 and a team of experienced professionals, the platform provides a secure and accessible opportunity for individuals and corporations to invest in property