(582, 'LendSecured', '/platformLogo/LendSecured.png', '[\"Latvia\"]', '[\"P2P lending\"]', '[\"Farming\"]', '2019', '0000000', '[\"English\",\"German\",\"Latvian\"]', NULL, 'https://lande.finance/?click_id=b17bc398-6bfa-46cd-9530-21ab927ca098&utm_source=circlewise&utm_medium=privateprogram&offer=LANDE&utm_campaign=CrowdSpace&promo_code=', '50 EUR', 'up to 14%', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'LendSecured is a crowdfunding platform based in Latvia that specializes in P2P lending for sustainable agricultural projects. Founded in 2019, LendSecured aims to support farmers by providing them with access to funding through their platform.\n\nThe platform offers investment opportunities for both natural and legal persons, allowing individuals and businesses to invest in agricultural projects. It focuses specifically on the farming industry, providing a unique investment avenue for those interested in supporting sustainable agriculture.\n\nLendSecured\'s website is available in multiple languages, including English, German, and Latvian, making it accessible to a wider range of investors. The minimum investment amount required is 50 EUR, making it affordable for individuals looking to diversify their investment portfolio.\n\nLendSecured advertises a potential return of up to 14%, which can be an attractive option for those seeking higher returns on their investments. By investing through LendSecured, individuals and businesses can contribute to the growth and development of sustainable farming projects while potentially benefiting from attractive returns.\n\nOverall, LendSecured serves as a bridge between farmers in need of funding and investors looking for sustainable investment opportunities in the farming industry.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 'Natural and legal persons', 'lendsecured', '2023-08-08 09:32:56', '2023-08-08 09:32:56'),
(583, 'Nibble', '/platformLogo/Nibble.png', '[\"Spain\"]', '[\"P2P lending\"]', '[\"SME\"]', '2019', '14831029', '[\"English\",\"Spanish\",\"Russian\",\"Deutsch\",\"Italian\"]', NULL, 'https://nibble.finance/', '10 EUR', '19%', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Nibble is a P2P crowdfunding platform based in Spain, specializing in SME investments. It was founded in 2019 and is part of the IT Smart Finance Group (ITSF), a financial conglomerate established in 2014 with a presence in Spain and Russia. The conglomerate has over 200 employees worldwide across its various companies.\n\nWith Nibble, individuals or legal entities with bank accounts in European countries have the opportunity to invest in SMEs through P2P lending. The platform offers a diverse range of investment opportunities and allows investors to start with a minimum investment of 10 EUR.\n\nNibble\'s website is available in multiple languages, including English, Spanish, Russian, Deutsch, and Italian, making it accessible to a wider audience. This global reach allows the platform to attract investors from different countries and create a diverse investment community.\n\nOne of the key factors of Nibble is their advertised return of 0.19, offering a potential return on investments. This can be an attractive option for individuals looking to grow their savings or diversify their investment portfolios.\n\nOverall, Nibble provides an inclusive and convenient platform for individuals or legal persons across Europe to invest in SMEs, with its easy-to-use website and low minimum investment requirement.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Any individual or legal person with a bank account in one of the European countries can become a Nibble investor.', 'nibble', '2023-08-08 09:32:56', '2023-08-08 09:32:56'),
(584, 'Lendermarket', '/platformLogo/Lendermarket.png', '[\"Ireland\"]', '[\"P2P lending\"]', '[\"Real estate\",\"SME\",\"Personal loans\"]', '2019', NULL, '[\"English\",\"French\",\"German\",\"Spanish\"]', NULL, 'https://lendermarket.com/?click_id=4ea76299-0977-49c8-9ce5-7be3996ba10e&utm_source=Affiliate&utm_medium=targetcircle&utm_campaign=CrowdSpace&partner_id=targetcircle&publisher_id=CrowdSpace', '10 EUR', '15.26%', 'N/A', '[\"Bank transfer\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Lendermarket is a crowdfunding platform based in Ireland that specializes in P2P lending. The platform allows individuals and institutions from around the world to invest in loans issued by digital consumer finance companies in various European countries. Lendermarket primarily focuses on three industries: real estate, SME, and personal loans.\n\nFounded in 2019, Lendermarket offers its services in multiple languages, including English, French, German, and Spanish. The platform\'s website provides more details about its operations and investment opportunities.\n\nInvestors can start with a minimum investment of 10 EUR and enjoy an advertised return of 15.26%. Lendermarket emphasizes the careful selection of loan issuers to ensure the quality and reliability of investment opportunities.\n\nLendermarket welcomes both individual investors and companies to participate in their platform. Individual investors need to meet certain criteria, such as being at least 18 years old, having a personal bank account in the European Economic Area, UK, or Switzerland, and completing a successful identity verification process. Organizations, including family trusts, partnerships, and limited liability companies, are required to have a bank account in the EEA, UK, or Switzerland.\n\nPotential investors should review the dropdown menu in the registration form to confirm if their country of residency and tax residency is included in the platform\'s offerings.', 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 1, 'We invite both individuals and companies to invest through the Lendermarket platform. Individual investors are required to:– be at least 18 years old,– have a personal bank account in the European Economic Area, UK or Switzerland,– and have their identity successfully verified by the Lendermarket team.Family trusts, partnerships, limited liability companies, and other organizations must have a bank account in the EEA, UK or Switzerland.Please check the dropdown menu in the registration form to confirm if your country of residency and tax residency is included.', 'lendermarket', '2023-08-08 09:32:56', '2023-08-08 09:32:56'),
(585, 'RE-LENDER', '/platformLogo/RE-LENDER.png', '[\"Italy\"]', '[\"P2P lending\"]', '[\"Real estate\",\"SME\"]', '2019', 'N/A', '[\"English\"]', NULL, 'https://www.relender.eu/?utm_source=affiliate&utm_medium=performoney&utm_campaign=1255', '50 EUR', 'N/A', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'RE-LENDER is a crowdfunding platform based in Italy that focuses on P2P lending in the real estate and SME industries. Founded in 2019, RE-LENDER aims to revitalize communities and their surroundings by raising funds for various projects. The platform offers its services in English, making it accessible to a wider audience.\n\nAs the world\'s first \"reconversion crowdfunding\" platform, RE-LENDER goes beyond traditional crowdfunding by emphasizing the importance of giving new life to communities. The company provides a highly-rated advisory service, ensuring that all aspects of the complex real estate and SME initiatives are designed and managed effectively.\n\nWhile the minimum investment required is 50 EUR, the advertised return on investments is not specified. However, RE-LENDER offers an opportunity for both personal and corporate investors to participate in these projects. By investing through the platform, individuals and businesses can contribute to the transformation and revitalization of various communities and their surrounding areas.\n\nOverall, RE-LENDER is a unique crowdfunding platform that combines P2P lending with a focus on community development. With its advisory services and dedication to reconversion, the platform offers an opportunity for investors to make a positive impact while potentially earning returns on their investments.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Personal, Corporate', 're-lender', '2023-08-08 09:32:56', '2023-08-08 09:32:56'),
(586, 'Recrowd', '/platformLogo/Recrowd.png', '[\"Italy\"]', '[\"Equity\"]', '[\"Real estate\"]', '2018', '2019071202', '[\"English\",\"Italian\"]', NULL, 'https://www.recrowd.com/it/home?custom=1020583f97648d66acaa5130b55547%7C1255%7C%7C%7C%7C%7C%7C%7C', '250 EUR', 'N/A', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Recrowd is a real estate crowdfunding platform based in Italy. Founded in 2018, it offers equity investments in the real estate industry. The platform aims to provide individuals and corporations with the opportunity to invest their savings in an alternative way, even if they do not have large capital.\n\nRecrowd supports both English and Italian languages, making it accessible to a wider range of investors. Their website, available at https://www.recrowd.com/it/home?custom=1020583f97648d66acaa5130b55547%7C1255%7C%7C%7C%7C%7C%7C%7C, provides information and resources for potential investors.\n\nThe minimum investment on Recrowd is 250 EUR, allowing investors to participate even with modest amounts. However, the advertised return on investment is not specified.\n\nThe platform specializes in real estate crowdfunding, leveraging lending crowdfunding to provide investors with a straightforward and highly profitable asset. This allows individuals and corporations to diversify their investment portfolios and potentially generate income from the real estate market.\n\nRecrowd welcomes both personal and corporate investors, expanding its appeal to a broader audience. Whether individuals are looking to invest their personal savings or corporations are seeking alternative investment opportunities, Recrowd offers a platform to explore the real estate crowdfunding sector.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Personal, Сorporate', 'recrowd', '2023-08-08 09:32:56', '2023-08-08 09:32:56'),
(587, 'Reinvest24', '/platformLogo/Reinvest24.png', '[\"Estonia\"]', '[\"P2P lending\"]', '[\"Real estate\"]', '2017', 'None yet', '[\"English\",\"Spanish\",\"German\",\"Estonian\"]', NULL, 'https://www.reinvest24.com/en?tc_id=9f46397e-8050-40a4-bff1-210f8e9bbfbb', '1 EUR', '14%', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Reinvest24 is a crowdfunding platform based in Estonia that specializes in P2P lending for real estate investments. Founded in 2017, the platform offers a range of investment opportunities in the real estate industry, including rental properties, development projects, and real estate backed loans. \n\nOne of the key features of Reinvest24 is its international reach, allowing investors to diversify their portfolio across five different European countries: Estonia, Latvia, Moldova, Spain, and Germany. This provides investors with the opportunity to tap into various real estate markets and potentially benefit from different market conditions and growth potentials.\n\nThe platform is accessible to investors from around the world, with its website available in multiple languages including English, Spanish, German, and Estonian. It caters to both private individuals and legal entities interested in real estate investments.\n\nReinvest24 offers a low barrier to entry, with a minimum investment requirement of just 1 EUR. This makes it accessible to a wide range of investors, regardless of their financial capacity. \n\nThe platform advertises a return of 0.14, indicating the potential annual return on investment. However, it\'s important to note that returns on investments in real estate are subject to market conditions and individual project performance.\n\nOverall, Reinvest24 provides investors with a user-friendly platform to participate in P2P lending for real estate projects across Europe, offering the potential for diversification and attractive returns.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 'Private persons and legal entities', 'reinvest24', '2023-08-08 09:32:56', '2023-08-08 09:32:56'),
(588, 'Goparity', '/platformLogo/Goparity.png', '[\"Portugal\"]', '[\"Debt\",\"P2P lending\"]', '[\"SME\",\"Sustainability\",\"Green energy\",\"Social cause\",\"Farming\",\"Maritime\"]', '2017', 'N/A', '[\"English\",\"Spanish\",\"Portuguese\"]', NULL, 'https://app.goparity.com/en/signup?click_id=65dfcdde-09fc-482f-b5d5-62bc692d58db&utm_source=affiliate&utm_medium=circlewise&utm_campaign=CrowdSpace', '5 EUR', '6%', 'N/A', '[\"Credit card\",\"Bank transfer\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'GoParity is a crowdfunding platform based in Portugal that focuses on debt-based P2P lending. It was founded in 2017 and primarily caters to the SME industry, with a specific emphasis on sustainability, green energy, social causes, farming, and maritime projects. \n\nThe platform offers an opportunity for individuals and institutions to invest in sustainable projects and earn competitive returns starting from a minimum investment of €5. GoParity aims to simplify the investment process and connect citizens who are interested in supporting environmentally friendly initiatives. \n\nWith a multilingual interface available in English, Spanish, and Portuguese, the platform ensures accessibility to a wider audience. Investors can browse through the available projects and choose the ones they are interested in contributing to. The returns on investment are advertised at 0.06, making it an attractive option for individuals looking to diversify their investment portfolio and support impactful ventures. \n\nGoParity welcomes both private investors and institutional investors, providing an inclusive investment opportunity for anyone interested in supporting sustainable projects in various sectors. By investing as little as €5, investors can contribute towards the overall loan value of the projects they choose to support. \n\nOverall, GoParity offers a user-friendly and accessible platform for individuals and institutions to invest in sustainable projects and make a positive impact on the environment and society.', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 'Any investor — either a private investor or an institution — can invest from € 5 in any of our projects open to funding, contributing towards the overall loan value.', 'goparity', '2023-08-08 09:32:56', '2023-08-08 09:32:56'),
(589, 'Debitum Network', '/platformLogo/Debitum Network.png', '[\"Lithuania\"]', '[\"P2P lending\"]', '[\"SME\"]', '2017', '42103092209', NULL, NULL, 'https://debitum.network/?utm_source=targetcircle&utm_medium=affiliate&utm_campaign=2022Q3&utm_term=&utm_content=pa6833&tmt_data=61851327-27eb-4557-8e82-c2af7fc34999', '500 EUR', '9.97%', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Debitum Network is a crowdfunding platform based in Lithuania that specializes in peer-to-peer lending for small and medium-sized enterprises (SMEs). Founded in 2017, Debitum Network offers an independent and decentralized financing ecosystem that connects businesses with capital to meet their financing and growth needs.\n\nThe platform focuses on providing businesses with an alternative financing solution, utilizing modern technology to streamline the lending process. Debitum Network boasts transparency and aims to create a fair and open environment for all participants. \n\nInvestors can participate in P2P lending on the platform, with a minimum investment of 500 EUR. The advertised return for investments on Debitum Network is 9.97%, which makes it an attractive option for individuals and companies looking to diversify their investment portfolios.\n\nDebitum Network welcomes both personal and corporate investors, providing them with the opportunity to support SMEs and earn returns on their investments. Through the platform, investors can contribute to the growth and development of businesses in various sectors.\n\nTo learn more about Debitum Network or to get involved in P2P lending, interested individuals can visit their website at https://debitum.network.', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Personal, Corporate', 'debitumnetwork', '2023-08-08 09:32:56', '2023-08-08 09:32:56'),
(590, 'Profitus', '/platformLogo/Profitus.png', '[\"Lithuania\"]', '[\"P2P lending\"]', '[\"Real estate\"]', '2017', '304570552', '[\"English\",\"Lithuanian\",\"German\"]', NULL, 'https://ss.profitus.com/register?utm_source=TargetCircle&utm_medium=referral&click_id=5bf5e64b-7a2c-4e9f-b1f2-2d6b11d65991', '100 EUR', '7-14%', 'N/A', '[\"N/A\"]', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Profitus is a crowdfunding platform based in Lithuania that specializes in peer-to-peer lending for real estate investments. Founded in 2017, Profitus aims to make investment opportunities accessible to everyone by allowing investments to start as low as 100 EUR. The platform operates 24/7 and offers an advertised return ranging from 7% to 14%.\n\nProfitus provides a secure investment environment by ensuring that investments are backed by collateral such as real estate and other assets. This helps to mitigate risks and gives investors peace of mind. As a licensed platform supervised by the Bank of Lithuania, Profitus is committed to verifying the investment knowledge and identity of its users. In some cases, a justification of the source of income may be required for larger investments.\n\nThe platform supports multiple languages including English, Lithuanian, and German, making it accessible to a wide range of investors. Both natural and legal persons are eligible to invest, and Profitus emphasizes that even small amounts can be invested.\n\nWith its user-friendly website and dedication to transparency and security, Profitus offers an attractive platform for individuals looking to invest in real estate through peer-to-peer lending.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 'Both natural and legal persons can. You can start investing even in small amounts. As a licensed platform under the supervision of the Bank of Lithuania, we need to verify your investment knowledge and properly identify you after the registration. If you invest more, we may ask you to justify your source of income.', 'profitus', '2023-08-08 09:32:56', '2023-08-08 09:32:56'),
(591, 'Rendity', '/platformLogo/Rendity.png', '[\"Austria\",\"Germany\",\"Switzerland\"]', '[\"Equity\",\"Debt\"]', '[\"Real estate\"]', '2015', 'FN 438425 v', '[\"English\",\"German\"]', NULL, 'https://rendity.com/en?click_id=982db84b-3a79-4c3c-a0da-c595486d9b76', '100 EUR', '8.5%', 'N/A', '[\"Credit card\",\"Bank transfer\"]', 'N/A', '19 months', 'Rendity is a crowdfunding platform that operates in Austria, Germany, and Switzerland. Founded in 2015, it specializes in real estate investments and offers two types of investment opportunities: equity and debt. The platform is available in English and German, catering to a wide range of investors.\n\nRendity stands out in the European real estate market as a pioneer and aims to revolutionize the way people invest in real estate. It provides investors with the ability to create customized portfolios by selecting from a diverse range of real estate projects.\n\nTo participate, individuals and companies must have a bank account within the European Union (EU) and be at least 18 years old. The minimum investment required is 100 EUR, making it accessible to a wide range of investors.\n\nOne of the key attractions of Rendity is the advertised return of 8.5%, which provides the potential for significant profits for those who choose to invest in the platform. The platform\'s website offers comprehensive information about the investment opportunities available and allows potential investors to learn more about the projects.\n\nOverall, Rendity is a reputable crowdfunding platform that offers an innovative approach to investing in real estate. With its user-friendly website, diverse portfolio options, and attractive returns, it provides a compelling platform for individuals and companies looking to invest in the real estate market within Austria, Germany, and Switzerland.', 1, 0, 1, 1, 0, 1, 'Any person with a bank account within the European Union (EU) can make investments on our platform upon reaching the age of 18.Companies with a bank account within the European Union (EU) can also invest.', 'rendity', '2023-08-08 09:32:56', '2023-08-08 09:32:56');
